Products.Description:
Our organic super green soup is made with passion, care and..
All natural ingredients - nothing added so you know it's Just Food.

Welcome to our new HiLo High protein, Low Fat range of soups. We have developed this super healthy range of soups in response to the huge customer demand for higher protein, lower fat, all natural, yet very tasty food solutions. If you are interested in losing weight, maintaining weight, are physically active, or are concerned about muscle mass loss, our new HiLo range will be a welcome addition to your diet.
Enriched with protein rich chicken broth, and packed with healthy veggies, these soups are delicious for lunch time or any time! We have managed to squeeze two portions of super greens into this soup, with the trio of peas, spinach and broccoli being among the most nutrient dense foods available, supplying protein, folate and iron, to name just a few of the goodies they contain.
Deirdre Hilliard
